  <p><b>SHR ConditionTopic Extension</b></p>
  <p>A condition, independent of context. 'Condition' is interpreted broadly to include disorder, abnormality, problem, injury, complaint, functionality, concern, illness, disease, ailment, sickness, affliction, upset, difficulty, disorder, symptom, worry, or trouble, independent of context.
CIMI deviation: AnatomicalLocation is included here, rather than being a property of FindingSiteAssertionTopic, since it is a common property of conditions. Severity, diseasePhase, periodicity, and other properites of an actual observed condition belong in ConditionPresenceContext.</p>
</div>
